{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-13", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-13</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> OpenClaw Faces High-Risk Vulnerability, Attackers Can Trigger via WhatsApp Messages<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenClaw存在高風險弱點，攻擊者可透過WhatsApp外部訊息觸發</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Researchers found vulnerabilities in the popular open-source AI agent platform OpenClaw, which has 381,000 GitHub stars and 100,000 daily users. Attackers can exploit disguised WhatsApp debug requests to execute arbitrary code on OpenClaw hosts.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員在擁有38.1萬顆GitHub星星、每日10萬用戶的開源AI代理平台OpenClaw中發現資安弱點，攻擊者可利用偽裝成除錯請求的WhatsApp訊息，於主機上執行任意程式碼。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177241\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Lorde Says Ray-Ban Meta AI Glasses Are 'Not Sexy'<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Lorde公開批評Ray-Ban Meta AI眼鏡「不性感」</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Singer Lorde criticized AI glasses during her performance at the Real Cool Festival in Madrid, likely referencing festival sponsor Ray-Ban's collaboration with Meta on AI-powered eyewear.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">歌手Lorde在馬德里Real Cool音樂節演出時公開批評AI眼鏡，被認為是暗指贊助商Ray-Ban與Meta合作推出的AI眼鏡產品。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/964539/lorde-says-ray-ban-meta-ai-glasses-are-not-sexy\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> Apple's Failed Self-Driving Car Program Left a Legacy of Powerful AI Chips<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Apple自駕車計畫雖告終，卻催生強大AI晶片技術</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Apple's self-driving car project never launched, but the need for powerful on-device AI processing it identified early on shaped the company's chips into the strong AI performers they are today.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Apple的自駕車計畫雖未成功推出，但當初為此開發的強大裝置端AI運算需求，意外造就了現今Apple晶片優異的AI效能。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tech/964519/apple-silicon-self-driving-car-ai-m7-ultra\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> The Fight Against AI Data Centers Is Just Beginning<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">反對AI資料中心的抗爭才剛開始</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">As the AI boom drives massive data center expansion, communities and advocacy groups are increasingly pushing back against the infrastructure buildout that threatens local resources.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">隨著AI熱潮帶動資料中心大規模擴張，社區與倡議團體對這波基礎建設的反彈聲浪日益升高。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/column/963346/ai-data-centers-fight\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Scientists' Side Hustle? Using AI and Quantum Computing to Generate New Peptides<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">科學家的副業：用AI與量子運算開發新型胜肽藥物</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Researchers combined limited funding and spare time to demonstrate how quantum computing can aid drug development for underserved populations and rare diseases.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員利用有限的資金與業餘時間，展示量子運算如何協助開發藥物，造福弱勢族群與罕見疾病患者。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/scientists-using-ai-and-quantum-computing-to-generate-new-peptides/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> OpenAI Bets on Families as ChatGPT Goes Deeper Into Households<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI押注家庭市場，讓ChatGPT深入家戶生活</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI is hiring a dedicated product manager to build ChatGPT experiences tailored for families, caregivers, and older adults, according to a job posting.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">根據徵才公告，OpenAI正招募專屬產品經理，為家庭、照顧者與長者打造專屬的ChatGPT體驗。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/11/openai-bets-on-families-as-chatgpt-goes-deeper-into-households/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}